      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-190 Analyze Supplier’s Results
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-935BF13A-1E9C-404C-A32E-68DCDE3D96DC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Parameter examples:
*Contracts
*Spends
*SLA's
*Risk and responsibilities
*Contract P-Specs</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3D278360-0F9D-4AE2-925B-5668A6D9A320" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description-
This is the process of reviewing the software-generated vendor evaluation data to determine how close suppliers adhered to previously established performance standards. In this process, superior performers and poor performers would be identified and informed of their status,</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9CE02C46-DD1A-4075-B0E7-ED9B78863882" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Boundary apps 
•Online supplier report card
•The Grid
•Graphite
•Supplier 360 (SAM, SDM)
•Contract governance reports</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3227885F-E802-493C-81B3-FAEF776BC5C3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
